FAQs

FAQs

Frequently Asked Questions

What is HVLA Thrust & Spinal Manipulation?

It’s a hands-on technique that involves a high-velocity, low-amplitude thrust to adjust the spine, aiming to restore mobility and alleviate pain.

Is the treatment safe?

Yes, when performed by a certified expert like Dr. Joisher, it’s a safe and effective method for various musculoskeletal issues.

How many sessions will I need?

The number of sessions varies based on individual conditions. Dr. Joisher will assess and recommend a personalized treatment plan.
